import math

def find_max_gcd_in_range(n: int) -> int:
    """
    Finds the maximum possible greatest common divisor (GCD) of any pair of distinct integers
    in the range from 1 to n (inclusive).

    Parameters:
    n (int): The upper limit of the range (inclusive).

    Returns:
    int: The maximum possible GCD of any pair of distinct integers in the range.
    """
    return int(math.floor(n / 2))
